passengers  Equipment preferences   Please call UIC Dispatch at (312) 99 6-2842 with any questions.   Name * Required   First   Last  Department * Required Building * Required Valid Email * Required   Phone * Required Name of Site Contact * Required    First     Last   Cell Number for Site Contact * Required Date Request Submitted - must be mm/dd/yyyy format * Required   Date Format: MM slash DD slash YYYY   Date of Chauffeur Service - must be mm/dd/yyyy format * Required   Date Format: MM slash DD slash YYYY   Multiple Days Required? * Required Yes No Number of Passengers * Required Vehicle Type * Required   Sedan    15 Passenger Van    25 Passenger Bus    Full Size Bus    Paratransit Vehicle    Special Equipment Considerations    Other  Description of Service (Locations, Pickup/Return times) * Required Assisted/ Accessible Boarding Required? * Required Yes No Unknown Please List Any Special Circumstances Email This field is for validation purposes and should be left unchanged.                This iframe contains the logic required to handle Ajax powered Gravity Forms.      Vehicles    Back to main content           CARS    Chauffeur Service               UIC Logo        Transportation         Policies    Web Privacy Notice      Related Links    Facilities Management    Office of the Vice Chancellor of Administrative Services         Contact   1351 South Morgan Street  Phone: (312) 996-2842  Fax: (312) 996-0165  rides@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings     